revxrsal.commands.exception

Annotation Type ThrowableFromCommand


  • @Inherited
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ThrowableFromCommand
    Marks an exception class as throwable from inside the command. Any exceptions annotated with this annotation will be unwrapped from CommandInvocationException. *
    See Also:
    CommandInvocationException
